{"tid":864682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實明日大嶼同150單程證有冇關係？","createTime":"2018-10-16T11:21:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-17T05:58:40.000Z","uid":55200,"like":0,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9fb3ef2b177d6aa4af61ec3ed4bc3b8e7a10422d","tid":864682,"uid":55200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T11:21:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180402/20350140\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180402%2F20350140&d=s6l9MFVJgpHrcry9F5uOIE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=688cd6db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180402%2F20350140&h=f7897994\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180402/20350140</a><br />\n<br />\n蘋果條片講哂，其本上黎香港既大陸人，好多都被香港人同化左。<br />\n<br />\n總人口在香港出世比率仲持續上升。<br />\n<br />\n連登仔點睇？想聽下你地點講"},{"pid":"e5cc7ea6e1d806f5594746268484853da79956dd","tid":864682,"uid":55200,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T11:49:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a5d1df8f540d1999f72f9d63562490ce94231a28","tid":864682,"uid":207563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T11:58:23.000Z","msg":"大陸出世個佔比都唔少<br />\n不過我認為150個唔係問題核心<br />\n人口過多先係，但政府為左經濟增長，只會一定催谷人<br />\n就算有無呢150個人口都係要不斷上升，土地問題唔會解決到"},{"pid":"16e9f6757f0265d6e0ec7ebe6ef17f3b206000a5","tid":864682,"uid":99205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T12:06:54.000Z","msg":"本港出世<br />\n但父母唔係香港成長?"},{"pid":"b98708f840495b90780ca6df3735cc659824fd10","tid":864682,"uid":55200,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"a5d1df8f540d1999f72f9d63562490ce94231a28","tid":864682,"uid":207563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T11:58:23.000Z","msg":"大陸出世個佔比都唔少<br />\n不過我認為150個唔係問題核心<br />\n人口過多先係，但政府為左經濟增長，只會一定催谷人<br />\n就算有無呢150個人口都係要不斷上升，土地問題唔會解決到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T12:32:14.000Z","msg":"Agger, 我反而覺得太多人用表面既數字就立論，缺乏深度既討論好可怕，簡單啲講就係民智未開。"},{"pid":"a04a8d71e48196c7257ccb0ff2b8d223f5d2d903","tid":864682,"uid":44391,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T12:38:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"17ae929f5deb68b72c0b55c6de4fad74b46e8d27","tid":864682,"uid":207563,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T12:41:19.000Z","msg":"唔講技術問題，例如要起幾錢，個島會唔會沉，如果要滿足日後香港人口增長，經濟發展，要人住得好，1700公頃都唔會夠。人口太多太逼既惡果今日港鐵事故已經體現得到。<br />\n有一個事實係，無論點用棕地，軍用地，就算限制150個新移民名額，長遠土地都係唔夠，除非香港人唔生仔。填海係眾多選擇中最可行一個。"},{"pid":"4f037709e665490809e15dbc83060932be1eb874","tid":864682,"uid":48083,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T12:44:59.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n150*365=54,750<br />\n20年就一百萬人<br />\n要幾多樓先夠？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有醫療交通教育社會福利？<br />\n仲未計其他專才"},{"pid":"006428d2579f9083c8b666a78760e3ae27c4fd67","tid":864682,"uid":57513,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T12:46:33.000Z","msg":"5毛post扮討論"},{"pid":"797dafc6a3a67714006b8415357a13f49f7c477a","tid":864682,"uid":55200,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"006428d2579f9083c8b666a78760e3ae27c4fd67","tid":864682,"uid":57513,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T12:46:33.000Z","msg":"5毛post扮討論"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T15:29:44.000Z","msg":"依家係咪同連登主流意見唔同，就有需要俾人打做5毛，咁同共產黨有咩分別"},{"pid":"28c86e99ef78487a22bac2e4b4e26d4c871397e7","tid":864682,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a04a8d71e48196c7257ccb0ff2b8d223f5d2d903","tid":864682,"uid":44391,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T12:38:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T15:32:26.000Z","msg":"應該係生活喺平行時空"},{"pid":"80fd276dcbc37c876c2cd7b5fc451ae074d0f60e","tid":864682,"uid":47659,"like":4,"disl